<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,152,611]" pageId="3" pageNumber="292">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,351,152,179]" pageId="3" pageNumber="292">Colouration.</emphasis>
Body yellowish green (probably green when alive). Eyes brown. Disc of pronotum with 1 pair of longitudinally yellow stripes. Spines of legs black brown.
</paragraph>
